---
title: Grilled Maple-Chipotle Chicken Breast with Creamy Grilled Potato Salad and Peas
description: Sweet and smoky chicken  is everything we want for hot summer days! Our twist on a classic potato side dish takes the spuds to the grill before mixing in a creamy dressing with a hint of sweetness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R207_W24_FR_QFR20161987-9_Main__11low-86e5ea82.jpg
